Consumer Price Index in Macao Down Slightly
MACAO , September 21 ( Xinhua ) -- The composite consumer price index for August in Macao decreased by 0.5 percent compared with July , according to figures released Monday by the Macao Census and Statistics Department .
The prices of clothing , daily necessities , food and beverage went down slightly while the cost of medical care , medicine , transport and telecommunication rose a little bit .
In comparison with August last year , the price index decreased by 1.3 percent .
Between January and August this year , the average composite consumer price index increased by one percent over the same period of last year .
